text: Warde V. Nichols (born March 23, 1969) was a member of the Arizona House of Representatives from 2003 through 2011. He was first elected to the House in November 2002, and was re-elected three times, in 2004, 2006, and 2008. He was ineligible to run again in 2010 due to Arizona's term limits. ==References== Category:Arizona Republicans Category:Members of the Arizona House of Representatives Category:1969 births Category:Living people
